honduras , whereby the state 's weapons go to the highest bidder rather than being used in the national interest
this when the regional military training and security center was created exclusively to train 10,000 salvadoran troops -- the same army that invaded us in 1969
those who are demanding the defense of sovereignty and territorial integrity
